org.mmbase.streams.createcaches

Class TranscoderResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mmbase.streams.createcaches.Result
      • org.mmbase.streams.createcaches.TranscoderResult

  • class TranscoderResult
extends Result
    Container for the result of a JobDefinition. This is the result of an actual transcoding. This means that it does have a 'destination' node getDestination() and URI getOut().
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Michiel Meeuwissen
